Problem Statement
========================================================
left: 60%
font-family: 'Times New Roman'
transition: rotate
<p style="font-size:26px; color:#1a1a1a;">
- E-commerce business is thriving over the years especially during this pandemic period. More sellers are joining the e-commerce platform such as Shopee.<br>
<br>
- Therefore, sometimes there are abundant of choices available for the same item from different sellers.<br>
<br>
- Shoppers might feel overwhelmed by the number of options they encountered when shopping online.<br>
<br>
- Shoppers end up spending long time researching for the best quality products often through reviews and ratings, resulting in information overload. This experience may lead shoppers to a state of indecision.</p>
