Reflection
========================================================
font-family: 'Times New Roman'

Limitations: Chicken & Egg problem 
--------------------------------------------------------
Recommendations are based on customers' feedback and rating.

Biasness:
--------------------------------------------------------
New shop has less chances to get recommendation because suggestion are made based on input such as total unit sales, number of reviews and rating tags.

Future Improvements:
--------------------------------------------------------
-Scrape real-time data for a more accurate suggestion<br>
-Develop a neutral algo that rate based on reviews and buyer tags without the influence of number of items sold.



